sentences: Natalia Sokolovskaya (Russian: Наталья Соколовская; born in June, 1989) is a Russian pianist and composer.
She also appeared on Guy Bacos's 2017 albums Christmas Variations and Mourning, Elegy, and Others.
2008 - Camillo Togni Competition, Italy - first prizeSokolovskaya has won numerous prizes including at the Dudley Yamaha International Piano Competition (UK 2014), Wells (UK) etc.
She won a special prize at the First German Piano Open Competition (2016).
